WEBVTT

00:13:29.120 --> 00:13:31.565
to protect the security of their countries

00:13:31.589 --> 00:13:32.740
and their people.

00:13:32.764 --> 00:13:35.687
But if you say, like that,

00:13:35.711 --> 00:13:38.217
in the US or in any European country,

00:13:38.241 --> 00:13:42.187
"We are going to close our doors
to Muslim refugees,"

00:13:42.211 --> 00:13:45.323
what you are saying
is the best possible help

00:13:45.347 --> 00:13:47.757
for the propaganda
of terrorist organizations.

00:13:48.146 --> 00:13:49.758
Because what you are saying --

00:13:49.782 --> 00:13:55.357
(Applause)

00:13:55.381 --> 00:14:00.964
What you are saying will be heard
by all the Muslims in your own country,